<h1 id='downloads'>Repository, Downloads and Packages</h1>

<dl>
<dt><a href='@MAINPAGE@'>Project page</a></dt>
<dd>The main project page</dd>

<dt><a
href="@DOWNLOAD@">Releases</a></dt>
<dd>Where to get release tarballs</dd>

